    "description": {
      "value": "<h2></b>Description</b></h2></p><p>The front of this +1 bashing heavy steel shield looks as though it is crafted from hundreds of bits of rubble and larger stones. When used to make a shield bash attack, stones fall from shield and cling to the target of the shield bash. The target must succeed at a DC 14 Fortitude saving throw or be entangled for 1d4 rounds. Once per day on command, the target's wielder can choose to petrify the target of a shield bash instead. The target must succeed at a DC 16 Fortitude saving throw or become petrified for 1 minute.<br><p><b>Base Item:</b> +1 bashing heavy steel shield</p><h3><b>Requirements</b></h3><p>Craft Magic Arms and Armor, bull's strength, shape stone, flesh to stone</p><h3><b>Source: </b></h3>Ultimate Equipment",
